sql_fr_run: with tmp (select abs((cur_cnt-prv_cnt)/metric*100) as metric from (select count(1) as cur_cnt, 'Unit' as field_name from (select * from com_us_lake.dagg_bax_comp cmp join com_us_lake.udef_ndc_hier ndc on cmp.ndc_number = ndc.ndc_code_10digit union select * from com_us_lake.dagg_bax_comp cmp join com_us_lake.udef_ndc_hier ndc on cmp.ndc_number = ndc.ndc_code_11digit) pa where cmp.aud_upd_dts >= date_add(date_trunc('DD',current_date),-1) and upper(level_1_sales_force) = 'HEMATOLOGY') cur cross join (select prv_count as prv_cnt, metric, field_name from com_us_lake.dq_count_table where rule_key = 911) prv on cur.field_name=prv.field_name) select * from tmp

with tmp (select abs((cur_cnt-prv_cnt)/metric*100) as metric from (select count(1) as cur_cnt, 'Unit' as field_name from (select * from com_us_lake.dagg_bax_dispense_file cmp join com_us_lake.udef_ndc_hier ndc on cmp.ndc_number = ndc.ndc_code_10digit union select * from com_us_lake.dagg_bax_dispense_file cmp join com_us_lake.udef_ndc_hier ndc on cmp.ndc_number = ndc.ndc_code_11digit) pa where cmp.aud_upd_dts >= date_add(date_trunc('DD',current_date),-1) and upper(level_1_sales_force) = 'HEMATOLOGY') cur cross join (select prv_count as prv_cnt, metric, field_name from com_us_lake.dq_count_table where rule_key = 912) prv on cur.field_name=prv.field_name) select * from tmp
select case when metric > threshold then 1 else 0 end as res from corp_us_lake.dq_output_table where entity_id in ('dq_911','dq_912')
